The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, puzzles, reading
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, february, september, april
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, rowing, tennis
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the person eating plum is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
