 2. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
 3. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is the nigerian##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the dutch##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the thai##6
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
10. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the argentine##6
13. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8

.:: Answer ::.
