.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-15::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, cricket, volleyball, badminton
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, martial-arts, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, r&b, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, british, chinese, spanish
 1. the argentine is the argentine##1
 2. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
 3. the british is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
 4. the british is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
 8. the argentine is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
 9. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
10. the person watching western movies is on the right of the chinese##1
11. the fan of gospel is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
13. the spanish is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
14. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##8
15. the person who's sport is cricket is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
16. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Sport           | volleyball | cricket       | skiing      | badminton  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | martial-arts | western   | drama   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | r&b          | soul      | gospel  |
| Nationality   | british   | chinese      | argentine | spanish |

